            <!-- Introduction Card -->
            <div class="card mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="h4 card-title mb-3">Welcome</h2>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        This application helps you calculate taxable gains and losses from your investment activities according to UK tax rules.
                        It processes broker statements and applies normal trade matching rules to determine your tax obligations.
                    </p>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        The calculator assists with completing SA106 (Capital Gains) and SA108 (Income) tax forms by:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-3">
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">📊 Calculating capital gains and losses</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">💰 Reporting dividends and withholding tax</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">📈 Tracking Section 104 holdings</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">🔄 Handling corporate actions</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

