                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="card feature-card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="feature-icon">📤</div>
                                <h3 class="h5 card-title">2. Import Your Data</h3>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    Navigate to the <strong>Import/Export</strong> tab and upload your Interactive Brokers XML statement files.
                                </p>
                            </div>
