                                    <a href="https://github.com/alexpung/UK-Investment-tax-calculator/wiki" 
                                       class="link-styled" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                                        Wiki
                                    </a> for detailed information and guidance.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="card feature-card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
                                <h3 class="h5 card-title">4. Your Data is Private</h3>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                    All calculations happen in your browser using Blazor WebAssembly. Your data never leaves your device.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

